//  ░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░
//  ░                                                                        ░
//  ░    桜  ターミナル  ·  S A K U R A   T E R M I N A L                    ░
//  ░                                                                        ░
//  ░    A bar that feels like ink drying on washi paper.                    ░
//  ░    Quiet. Considered. Everything in its place.                         ░
//  ░                                                                        ░
//  ░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░
//
//  PALETTE — named after traditional Japanese pigments
//
//    Shiro      (白)   (252, 248, 241)  ← warm off-white / washi paper
//    Sumi       (墨)   ( 38,  32,  28)  ← deep ink black, not pure
//    Sakura     (桜)   (220, 130, 150)  ← muted dusty cherry blossom
//    Koke       (苔)   (110, 145, 100)  ← muted moss green
//    Tsuchi     (土)   (185, 160, 130)  ← warm earth / sand
//    Umi        (海)   ( 95, 145, 175)  ← muted sea blue
//    Kiri       (霧)   (210, 205, 195)  ← fog grey, for borders
//    Kakiiro    (柿色) (210, 105,  60)  ← persimmon orange, rare accent
//
//  PHILOSOPHY:
//    · Soft rounded corners (6px) — like worn paper edges
//    · No sharp contrast — everything breathes
//    · The bar sits BELOW the screen, floating, like a scroll unrolled
//    · Workspaces use kanji numerals
//    · Clock uses 12h format with Japanese period marker (午前/午後 implied by dot)
//    · One vivid accent (Kakiiro persimmon) used ONLY on hover — a surprise

BarConfig
(

    // ================= GENERAL =================
    general:
    (
        display: None,
        bar_position: Down,
        floating_space: 5,
        increased_exclusive_bar_zone: 0,
        bar_check_reload_interval_ms: Some(500),
        bar_side_spaces_size: 12,
        bar_size: (0, 36),
        bar_border_radius: (6., 6., 6., 6.),
        bar_border_size: 1.0,
        bar_border_color: RGB((185, 160, 130)),
        bar_background_color: RGBA((252, 248, 241, 100)),
        font_family: "Noto Serif CJK JP",
        font_style: "Bold",
        spacing_between_all_modules: 6,
        force_static_position_context_menu: None,
        left_modules: [CustomModule(0), HyprWorkspaces],
        center_modules: [Clock],
        right_modules: [CustomModule(1), Network, VolumeOutput, Tray],
    ),


    // ================= GENERAL STYLE =================
//    general_style:
//    (
//        general_padding: Some(0),
//        general_text_size: Some(15),
//        general_text_orientation: Some(Horizontal),
